::Battera::

She looked over at Grimmler. "We are here here for the peace talks.  
How can I help you?"  She looked back at CyberShark and kisses his 
cheek.  She smiled at him then turned to Grimmler.  "We are here to 
help get the talks started?  Did you want to help us with our mission 
and try to bring peace to the groups?"
